#section("Introduction")
This paper focuses on the improvement of the ReSet settings application. The
improvements cover a large variety of topics, including a plugin system/* @plugin_system */,
attending accessibility concerns in/* @accessibility */, creating a testing
framework for DBus functionality in/* @test_framework */, animations for the
ReSet user interface and creating a command line application to interface with
ReSet.


